                <head>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Editor’s Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>—For the final Conference texts on Allied Control Commission procedures in
                    Bulgaria, Hungary, and Rumania, as included in the Protocol and Communiqué, see
                        <hi rend="italic">post</hi>, <ref target="#pg_1494">pages 1494</ref>, <ref target="#pg_1511">1511</ref>. For the final Conference texts on the
                    conclusion of peace treaties and the establishment of diplomatic relations with
                    Bulgaria, Finland, Hungary, and Rumania and on freedom of the press in those
                    countries, as included in the Protocol and Communiqué, see <hi rend="italic">post</hi>, <ref target="#pg_1492">pages 1492</ref>, <ref target="#pg_1509">1509</ref>.</p>
            </div>
